{
  "text": "Parts [CITATION_1] and (3) of Thm. 1 are technical facts we will use repeatedly in the rest of the paper. Thm. 1(2) gives a fairly strong lower bound on R r,k . We give some consequences of Thm. 1(4) in the paragraph before Conjecture 1.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "17609886"
